Package eu.ebdit.duckapter.annotation

Annotation Types Summary
Alias Allows annotated method or property to has more potential names.
Constructor Declares that annotated method will be constructor for given class.
Factory Declares that annotated method will be factory class or constructor for given class.
Optional Declares that annotated method or all method of annotated interface needn't to be implemented.
Original Declares that annotated parameter must be compatibile with original class.
Property Declares that method is property getter/setter.
Static Declares that annotated method or all methods of annotated class must be accessed static.
